OL,6,FA teenage motorist who admitted
OL,7,Fcausing the deaths of three passengers
OL,8,Fin a two-car crash five weeks after he
OL,9,Fpassed his driving test has been
OL,10,Fsentenced.
OL,12,FSpencer lost control of the car
OL,13,Fbetween Chipping Campden and Shipston-
OL,14,Fon-Stour whilst on his way home from
OL,15,Fschool in April 2023.
OL,17,FHis passengers, Harry Purcell, 17,
OL,18,FMatilda "Tilly" Seccombe, 16, and
OL,19,FFrank Wormald, 16, all died.
